esource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, while \\\"F Around and Find Out\\\" is certainly an \\u00e0 la mode phrase nowadays, this wasn't the team's official name.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles took to X, formerly known as Twitter, after the July 30 press conference, confessing their moniker was motivated by an iconic television show from 1985 -Golden Girls.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.047483787190535e-20, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Okay on the real though.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The official team name is Golden Girls,\\\" she wrote.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The renowned sitcom watches actress Betty White and three older women through their days spent living together and gossiping in Miami, Florida.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2092, \"end\": 2103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Betty White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betty_White\"}, {\"begin\": 2191, \"end\": 2198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9996243406362302, \"rank\": 0.00026555953733363333, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To Biles and the rest of Team USA's 2024 women's gymnastics competitors, the concept of the show seemed to fit the current group.\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2330, \"entities